snippet.textDisplay: Happy to come away with a draw.  We're in a good position now going forward.  I am however slightly concerned that we've just lost two players.  Last season we ran out of gas and had to start playing untested youth players.  We could do with one or two more faces to give us the depth to compete to the end if that's what's ahead of us again.  I'm happy with the season so far but let's learn from last season and not leave ourselves open for another collapse!  MOT
